# Cursor IDE Rules — LTC Capital Partners

# Read CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md for full behavioral rules.
# This file provides a summary for Cursor's built-in AI features.

# Core Equation: Success = Efficient & Scalable Management of Failure Risks

# Before coding:
# 1. Check alignment in 1-ALIGN/
# 2. Check risks in 2-PLAN/risks/
# 3. Check drivers in 2-PLAN/drivers/

# During coding:
# - Sustainability: Handle errors gracefully, write tests, no single points of failure
# - Efficiency: Minimal code for maximum clarity
# - Scalability: No magic numbers, no hardcoded limits

# After coding:
# - Run quality gates in 3-EXECUTE/tests/quality-gates/
# - Document decisions in 1-ALIGN/decisions/

# Brand: Primary #004851, Secondary #F2C75C, Accent #9B1842
# Font: Tenorite (fallback: Calibri)
# See _shared/brand/ for full standards
